{"tid":1386590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱睇完有關監控燈柱","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:58:12.000Z","uid":143987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"18bb25fd1c25c04bbf5f3baa1c9236c5c2fe9147","tid":1386590,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"30位學警申請離職<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385471</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iN7ES3s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiN7ES3s.png&h=ed2d6cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話到碌野可以查到手機張卡行到邊<br />\n之前見到有巴打話開飛行可以避過佢<br />\n咁我地係唔係真係應該買多部手機 同太空卡<br />\n平時行動用嘅手機就開飛行模式  當要行動個陣<br />\n就到目的地時  平時個部就開飛行  <br />\n部行動用嘅手機就熄番飛行  正常使用<br />\n走嘅時候又調番轉開熄飛行<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以用咁嘅模式避開個碌野<br />\n（以上係假設開飛行可以避到碌柱）<br />\n<br />\n如果唔得嘅話 大家又有冇其他方法呢？"},{"pid":"b6ea67fb3ce5a6b56161b326fe9354cef4b81da0","tid":1386590,"uid":143987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:51:25.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n8月5日 我會罷工"},{"pid":"fb32861c655728ba67b9cc7be5ab4281a197fa7f","tid":1386590,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:52:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0e9d731c580c244373e11a7d22b36f4bd0ebc3b","tid":1386590,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c27815c1d4571c8b2788249fcd708735644c6116","tid":1386590,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:54:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6e389d9987985e21863af482ca55adddc6d5cfa","tid":1386590,"uid":265256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:58:12.000Z","msg":"push"}]}